<figureCitation box="[341,408,1826,1851]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="10.[151,250,1746,1768]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1723]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[151,1436,193,1725]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURE 3. Clavus rugizonatus Hervier, 1895. A, B. Possible syntype of Clavus rugizonatus MNHN IM – 2000 – 3204, Loyalty Islands, Lifou, 19.3 x 10.9 mm; C. Molecular voucher IM – 2009 – 19172, Philippines, Panglao Is, PANGLAO 2004 Stn. B 9, 9 ° 33.1 ' N 123 ° 44.0 ' E, 8 – 10 m; D. Narrow example, Loyalty Islands, Lifou, LIFOU 2000, Stn. 1425, 15.8 x 7.3 mm; E, F. New Caledonia, EXPÉDITION MONTROUZIER, Touho Stn. 1269, 18.3 x 8.0 mm; G, H. New Caledonia, LAGON, Stn. 755, Canala Sector, SL 22.8 mm; I. Protoconch, Loyalty Islands, Lifou, LIFOU 2000, Stn. 1424." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/286279/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
